<TR bgcolor="99cc99"><TD>
	Product Description
</TD><TD>
	Sprint ION is one of the nation’s first integrated communications systems for consumers, providing integrated local and long-distance voice services, multiple phone lines, advanced calling features (like Caller ID), high-speed Internet access, and customer-controllable features over a single connection to the home.
  
Sprint ION includes unlimited high-speed Internet (up to 8-million bits per second downstream) with five e-mail addresses and instant access (no dial-up), up to four voice/fax lines that can be used simultaneously, unlimited local calling and 750 minutes of Long Distance calling  (including domestic long-distance and IntraLATA toll calls).

To learn more about the service and sign up to be one of the charter customers, go to www.sprint.com/ION on the World Wide Web, or visit booth #5141.  

</TD></TR>		



																 																		
